headline.main: McAuley Closing In on New West Brom Deal
headline.print_headline: McAuley Closing In on New West Brom Deal

lead_paragraph: The head of a Syrian dissident group at peace talks in Geneva said on Friday that the United Nations was likely to conclude eight days of negotiations later in the day and outline an agenda, format and date for the next round.
